    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable commuter for someone who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the roof and a few minor dents along the passenger side. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need suspension work and a new set of tires in the near future. The interior is clean but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets.",
