      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the zenith of naturally aspirated S54 engineering. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a fully overhauled VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Structural integrity is guaranteed with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings throughout. The chassis is optimized with Bilstein PSS10 adjustable dampers, providing exceptional damping rates without compromising the factory geometry. Finished in Carbon Black with flawless Nappa leather, this example exhibits zero paint oxidation and a pristine underbody. Mechanically synchronized and aesthetically immaculate, it is a definitive driver\u2019s machine for the discerning purist.",
